	<h3><a href="/science/surfingscientist/whois.htm">Who is the Surfing&nbsp;Scientist?</a></h3>
	<p>Despite being as 'Aussie as', Ruben Meerman was actually born in Holland. He moved to Bundaberg, Queensland when he was 9 and started surfing a few years later.</p>
	<p>He decided to study physics at school in an attempt to sit next to a hot girl. Sadly, this didn't work but it was the beginning of another beautiful relationship&hellip;with science! <a href="/science/surfingscientist/whois.htm" style="text-decoration:underline;">Read&nbsp;more&raquo;</a></p>
